flowRoot.flowPara: It provides C++ classes to process and visualize
A single header file must be included in your own sources, defining only four new classes.
It handles up to 4-D datasets (multispectral volumetric images) with template pixel types.
It can use external libraries and user-defined plug-ins to extend its capabilities.
Multiple architectures are supported (Unix, Windows, MacOSX, *BSD,...)
It is an open-source project which can be used in commercial applications.
